<div class="container titulo">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h1 class="section-title">In development</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
        <% if notice %>
          <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
        <% end %>
        <% if alert %>
          <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
        <% end %>  
      </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8 offset-md-2">
      <img src="<%= image_path("Chloe Armor Concept.png") %>" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>Hey guys! We are developing our next game! It will be a platformer action game with lots of puzzles, skills, cool art and so much more.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
   <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>The game will be a very complete one, with many levels, enemies, characters and items so we will take our time developing it. For that reason we will upload content and news in this page to keep you guys updated.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>A new journey is upon us. This will be our hardest game till now. We are proving ourselfs with this game, but we hope it meets your expectations when we finish it!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>The game will have a lot of exciting things and we hope to have the demo ready later this year.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
   <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>Here you can find the latests videos showing the work done so far. Also, we will post the link for the demo here when it is ready.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>You can find posts of our blog with the latest news and information about this game below. We hope you participate and tell us your opinions and suggestions.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <p>Stay tuned!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="videoWrapper">
              <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wbuVAdjleCo" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allow="encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="videoWrapper">
              <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QYKTqISda5Q" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
      <h2 class="subtitle">From our blog</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="posts">
    <% @posts.each do |g| %>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
              <% @pictures = Picture.where("post_id" => g[:id]) %>
              <% if @pictures.empty? %>
                <%= link_to(image_tag(image_path("Placeholder.png")), g) %>
              <% else %>
                <%= link_to(image_tag(image_path(@pictures[0].image)), g) %>
              <% end %>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8">
              <h2><%= link_to g[:title], g %></h2>
              <div class="date">
                <small><%= g[:created_at].year %>-<%= g[:created_at].month %>-<%= g[:created_at].day %> &nbsp; &nbsp; by: <%= g.user[:username] %></small>
              </div>
              <% if g[:categories] %>
                <div class="categorias">
                  <h5>Categories: </h5>
                  <% g[:categories].each do |a| %>
                    <h6><%= a %></h6>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              <% end %>
              <% if g[:tags] %>
                <div class="etiquetas">
                  <h5>Tags: </h5>
                  <% g[:tags].each do |b| %>
                    <% if !b.include? "(o)" %>
                      <h6><%= b %></h6>
                    <% end %>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              <% end %>
              <p><%= simple_format(g[:description].slice(0,150) + "...") %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <hr>
        </div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12 paginacion">
        <%= paginate @posts %>
        <br>
        <%= page_entries_info @posts %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>